  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Preheat</strong> the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle</p>\r\n<p><strong>Strip</strong> the rosemary leaves from the stems and chop finely</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dissolve</strong> the stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> in 400ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(800ml)</span> of boiled water</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the millet and stock to a medium size pot</p>\r\n<p><strong>Bring</strong> to a boil with a lid, then reduce to a simmer, and cook for 20 min, or until the water is absorbed and there are holes on the surface</p>\r\n<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, pour the beetroot juice into a small pot for step 7</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cut</strong> each beetroot in half</p>\r\n<p><strong>Discard</strong> the tops and tails of the beans</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong> the pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> into chunky strips, discarding the seeds and pith</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> and cut the onion<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> into chunky pieces</p>\r\n<p><strong>Peel</strong> the garlic and slice finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the vegetables and garlic to a baking tray, drizzle with olive oil and half of the chopped rosemary</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Group the beetroot and onion together as the beetroot's liquid keeps the onions moist whilst cooking&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> with salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Oven-roast</strong> for 25-30 min, or until the vegetables are cooked and starting to char</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> the millet is cooked, add 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> (2 tbsp)</span> of butter and stir to melt</p>\r\n<p><strong>Then</strong> add 175ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(350ml)</span> of milk and mash through</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> the remaining rosemary and crumble in half the feta, then season with pepper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--5-x400.jpg",
