          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Pour</strong> the cheesy millet into an oven proof baking dish (alternatively, use individual ones)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Put</strong> it in the oven for 5 min, or until bubbling around the sides</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/435.-step--6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> the reserved beetroot juice and balsamic vinegar to a small pot</p>\r\n<p><strong>Heat</strong> on a medium heat, adding a pinch of sugar (optional)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Reduce</strong> by half, then remove from the heat and add a drizzle of olive oil- this is your warm dressing&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
